def meeting(rooms):
    return rooms.index("O") if "O" in rooms else "None available!"

def meeting(rooms):
    return next((i for i, r in enumerate(rooms) if r == 'O'), 'None available!')

def meeting(rooms):
    return [o  for o,v in enumerate(rooms) if v=='O'][0] if 'O' in rooms else 'None available!'

def meeting(rooms):
